text: The 1923 Maryland gubernatorial election was held on November 6, 1923. Incumbent Democrat Albert Ritchie defeated Republican nominee Alexander Armstrong with 55.97% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== Major party candidates *Albert Ritchie, Democratic *Alexander Armstrong, Republican Other candidates *William H. Champlin, Socialist *Verne L. Reynolds, Independent ===Results=== ==References== 1923 Maryland Gubernatorial
title: 1923 Maryland gubernatorial election
